The paper deals with the optimization of drawings of non-planar graphs, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The formulation of optimization criteria and the algorithmic question suggest that the paper may also belong to sub-categories such as data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), graph theory (cs.GT), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
